10: Stella... You're Stella too, aren't you?
13: Tell me—WHY are you doing this?!
35:
Is that the extent of your ability,
Adjudicus?
44: It's the same attack as before!
55:
Damn it... Why?! Why is the power of
the curse fading?!
58:
You knew naught but pity and
contempt for your kind—a people
beyond saving.
62:
If you had only continued down that
heinous path, you might have
succeeded in usurping me. In
becoming the next Lord of Shadow.
68:
But at some point you faltered—you
started to believe in them. To
believe that a people as miserable
as the fiends had a future.
69:
No fool who is enraptured by the
paltry promises of the light can
hope to receive the power of the
daemons.
73:
Come. Let us sink into the darkness,
together.
81:
The Antipode Lance... It's connected
to the world of the dead.
86:
We should be able to find others
there... Those who died believing in
the power of the light!
92:
Lilith, no!
The curse... It can affect humans too!
97:
Forces of the light! Grant us your
power!
103:
Wh-what is this place? Where am I?
I was fighting the—
119:
Make them suffer...
Show no mercy...
121:
An eye for an eye...
Take everything from them...
123:
Please, we beg you.
Kill them all...
129: Are these truly our fallen comrades?
134: Are you out there, Eric? Eric!
143:
Tell me, humans. Are you the same
as us? Frail and powerless, with
hatred burning in your hearts?
144:
Then join us.
Shut out the light and embrace the
darkness—make our common
dream a reality.
165:
I suppose this... is how my journey
finally ends.
169:
Princess Lilith... Take the others with
you...
Run, and never look back.
